has absolutely never ruined our land.

532
00:25:11,310 --> 00:25:11,960
Xiaoman,

533
00:25:12,420 --> 00:25:15,010
you grew up in Yin Village, that’s true.

534
00:25:15,640 --> 00:25:18,300
But now you get paid by
the archaeological team.

535
00:25:18,670 --> 00:25:20,550
Whoever gives you the food,
you watch their moods.

536
00:25:20,550 --> 00:25:22,030
Whoever pays you the salary,
you follow their rules.

537
00:25:22,030 --> 00:25:23,240
Everyone knows this.

538
00:25:23,270 --> 00:25:24,870
That's right, that's right.

539
00:25:25,920 --> 00:25:26,590
Xian,

540
00:25:26,920 --> 00:25:28,400
what do you mean by that?

541
00:25:28,880 --> 00:25:29,280
You...

542
00:25:30,000 --> 00:25:31,830
I would never lose my conscience

543
00:25:31,830 --> 00:25:32,960
just for a paycheck.

544
00:25:33,030 --> 00:25:34,490
If they did it, they did it.

545
00:25:34,790 --> 00:25:35,940
If they didn't, they didn't.

546
00:25:35,940 --> 00:25:38,000
